How to build libwavelet ?

    Welcome to read this file, and you are must be want to know how to
   build this library, and I will help you.

Preparations

    You must need installed, or POSIX similar system as like Linux or 
   MacOS-X with bash. If you are Windows, install M-SYS and MinGW-W64, or 
   MinGW bundle compile environment.
    And latest version of FFTW3 source code, and it must be configured and
   built & installed to your system by 'make install'.

And ?

    Just type 'make'. It will done for all when it has no problem. Makefile will makes 'out' directory and copies libwavelet.a and wavelet2s.h file.
